@startuml 01-single-node
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title Single Node MySQL Architecture

rectangle "Application" as app #LightBlue
database "MySQL\n(Single Instance)" as mysql #LightGreen {
    storage "InnoDB" as innodb
    storage "Binlog" as binlog
}
storage "Disk" as disk #LightGray

app --> mysql : Read/Write
mysql --> disk : Persist

note right of mysql
  **Problems:**
  - Single Point of Failure
  - Limited by single disk
  - No horizontal scaling
end note

@enduml
